stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Reading
    Reading --> CommandCheck: line read (top of input)
    CommandCheck --> Exit: quit / q / exit
    CommandCheck --> Reading: help / clear
    CommandCheck --> Accumulate: ordinary line
    Reading --> Accumulate: continuation line
    Accumulate --> Completeness: check_statement_completeness
    Completeness --> Reading: INCOMPLETE (continuation prompt)
    Completeness --> Discard: ERROR (discard pending input)
    Discard --> Reading
    Completeness --> Execute: COMPLETE (append to repl_history)
    Execute --> RunWholeHistory: run_script_mir over entire repl_history
    RunWholeHistory --> Rollback: result is ERROR
    Rollback --> Reading: truncate repl_history to saved length
    RunWholeHistory --> Display: success
    Display --> Reading: incremental prefix diff vs last_output
    Exit --> [*]
